{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "de4c6e5b-6a1b-44d4-b4ea-0f4f5df8f002",
        "name": "Dllni - Supermarket Owner Module",
        "description": "## Base URL and Prefix\n- Collection variable `{{baseUrl}}` defaults to `http://Dllni.test`.\n- Prefix: `/api/v1`.\n- Owner routes are under `/api/v1/store-owner/*`.\n\n## Authentication\n- All requests require Sanctum bearer token: `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`.\n\n## Props Format\n- Path props: `{order}`, `{product}`, `{store}` as `{{orderId}}`, `{{productId}}`, `{{storeId}}`.\n- Query props: dashboard and employee list use `storeId`; inventory reports mostly use `store_id`.\n- Validation errors: `{ \"message\": string, \"errors\": { \"field\": [string] } }`.\n\n## Common Enums\n- rejectionType: `out_of_stock | fake_order | other`\n- stock operation: `SET | INCREMENT | DECREMENT`\n\n## Notes\n- Store ownership scope is enforced server-side.\n- For employee forms, load permission ids from `/store-owner/permissions` first.",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "baseUrl",
            "value": "http://Dllni.test"
        },
        {
            "key": "token",
            "value": ""
        },
        {
            "key": "storeId",
            "value": "1"
        },
        {
            "key": "orderId",
            "value": "1"
        },
        {
            "key": "productId",
            "value": "1"
        },
        {
            "key": "staffId",
            "value": "1"
        }
    ],
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "Dashboard",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Store owner dashboard",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/store-owner/dashboard?storeId={{storeId}}",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "store-owner",
                                "dashboard"
                            ],
                            "query": [
                                {
                                    "key": "storeId",
                                    "value": "{{storeId}}"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Today metrics for selected store.\n\nQuery props:\n- storeId: integer (required)."
                    },
                    "response": [
                        {
                            "name": "200 OK - dashboard",
                            "status": "OK",
                            "code": 200,
                            "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
                            "header": [],
                            "cookie": [],
                            "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Dashboard data retrieved successfully.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"totalOrders\": 20,\n    \"completedOrders\": 7,\n    \"newOrders\": 5,\n    \"pendingOrders\": 8,\n    \"totalSales\": 4523.75\n  }\n}"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
